{"tid":1131703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中非婚姻惹人關注 揭肯雅人對中國存戒心","createTime":"2019-04-29T23:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T00:51:28.000Z","uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"32a6a23e442f2efe4937873f6cd01b67fff64547","tid":1131703,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:17:38.000Z","msg":"中國積極發展一帶一路，在非洲進行大批基建投資，不少中國工人都跟隨國家的發展步伐，其中一人來到肯雅首都奈羅比，卻在此遇到一生最愛，兩人並由來自香港的牧師主持婚禮。一段普普通通的中非婚姻，卻引起肯雅民眾關注，揭示當地民眾對中國「入侵」存有戒心。<br />\n<br />\n33歲來自廣東的工人梁永玉（Liang Yongyu，音譯）在肯雅生活了一段長時間，會說一點斯瓦希里語，他更在這裏遇到現在的太太卡倫（Karen Ngunjiri），兩人去年12月在肯雅山下、在200名賓客面前結為夫婦，卡倫笑說：「對肯雅人來說是一場小婚禮。」<br />\n<br />\n肯雅5,000萬人口中，8成都是基督徒，梁永玉就在當地參加一個由香港牧師舉辦的崇拜，這些活動都是以他的母語廣東話進行的。<br />\n<br />\n幾星期後，婚禮片段卻被人上載至網上，更在YouTube瘋傳，上載者寫道：「那場人人都在討論的婚禮。」卡倫至今仍不知道誰人上載短片，但一對新人結婚後幾個月走上街時，陌生人都仍然認得出他們。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，一段中非通婚惹人關注，有網民更留下恐怖留言。卡倫：「有些網上留言很可怕，尤其是來自肯雅人的，他們認為中國是來這裏偷走我們的工作，或是在殖民，所以有人說他們連肯雅的女人都偷走了。」<br />\n<br />\n根據官方數據顯示，在2017年，中國是肯雅最大的貿易夥伴；早於2014年，估計肯雅住有4萬名中國移民，但移民眾多引起磨擦。在2015年，一間中餐館據報禁止非洲食客在下午5時後入來，去年就有一名中國老闆，因為大罵當地人「猴子」而被驅逐出境。<br />\n<br />\n肯雅民眾憂慮國家欠下大筆中國債務，當地傳媒更形容幫忙建中資鐵路的肯雅工人，被中國人上司當成二等公民。不過，看過梁永玉與卡倫婚禮的反中網民，似乎看不出這段婚姻的可貴之處，與其說卡倫屈服於中國文化，倒不如說是梁永玉願意改變信仰，舉行基督教式的非洲婚禮，而這場婚禮只請了20名華人賓客，連他的媽媽也未有到場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GXoWBfv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGXoWBfv.png&h=8b948991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190429&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59542866\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190429%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59542866&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYgogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=0140a52b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190429%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59542866&h=5f020741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190429&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59542866</a>"},{"pid":"018b5b2efff25fa2dd0cbdca1e8c9f69b065f007","tid":1131703,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc1db06f0d96bd0286e31d3f9596f3998b627775","tid":1131703,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:24:47.000Z","msg":"食非洲雞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77dbaa4bf3a56e3d6148cd79388530372e3e2da7","tid":1131703,"uid":185022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:25:58.000Z","msg":"蝗禍已經蔓延至非洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265f93babf9d804c529ff1392732cc0d555e43ec","tid":1131703,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd9b25f20b191353da10e52dd23bb2a3f7ae3ff","tid":1131703,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:26:43.000Z","msg":"啲蝗落地生根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e05cef9018e1f28a71844a15715c8b20132ec3b","tid":1131703,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:33:02.000Z","msg":"香港耶撚生意做到肯亞"},{"pid":"5d102f830fd1ddb5d28d47641d322c14dd846531","tid":1131703,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:39:05.000Z","msg":"African 叉燒包"},{"pid":"4173b8325b3fa289e32e542e39dd3ddf20938d2d","tid":1131703,"uid":47259,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"77dbaa4bf3a56e3d6148cd79388530372e3e2da7","tid":1131703,"uid":185022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:25:58.000Z","msg":"蝗禍已經蔓延至非洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:44:26.000Z","msg":"蝗乜禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班生番自己攞嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />舐完著數想無代價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年老共入聯合國咪多得呢班仆街既票囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1256756f187726df3971f3ef8cb307fb127b0785","tid":1131703,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:51:28.000Z","msg":"屌黑妹咁識玩"}]}